rComments: A true gem. Hilarious in class.
My favourite professor. Makes the whole class comfortable with his calm demeanor and positive energy. The lectures are very informative and engaging.
Attendance is always taken so show up. Participation is important. Pretty chill and laid back.
Cases were archaic... from the 1980s. Very monotonous during lectures. Grading did not follow guidelines and no rational in grading criteria. Major disappointment to the program.

His marketing class is fun as he incorporates real business examples into the lectures and provides the class the opportunity to discuss concepts with peers. Very informative person to talk to outside of class as well. Unfortunately, the course is very memorization heavy, which makes it less enjoyable.
